Description:
2 x MATR Fungi food , chilli dip, teriyaki & spring onions. 
MATR Fungi food is plant based and made of five simple Danish ingredients: Potato, beetroot, lupin, split peas & oats. It is developed with fungi fermentation, which gives a juicy bite and deep umami flavour.
